are like mother and infant.

1366
01:41:38,876 --> 01:41:40,751
A healthy mother ensures
a healthy infant.

1367
01:41:49,293 --> 01:41:54,335
You made a statement that Rajpal
was with you till 12:30 at night?

1368
01:41:56,210 --> 01:41:58,793
