1381
01:42:34,793 --> 01:42:38,043
...that day Kanhaiya came
straight home from work.

1382
01:42:38,918 --> 01:42:41,626
Six of us sleep here...

1383
01:42:41,793 --> 01:42:44,626
so if he had gone out
and come in,

1384
