Narco test on the parents Sir.

1404
01:43:42,293 --> 01:43:44,043
Ramesh, did you enter
Shruti's room at night?

1405
01:43:45,043 --> 01:43:47,835
Did you tidy up the
sheets after the murder?

1406
01:43:48,460 --> 01:43:50,126
