- Please see what you can do.
This will be very difficult for me.-

1440
01:47:00,751 --> 01:47:02,835
This is what it is... Now you decide.

1441
01:47:32,001 --> 01:47:33,168
Thank you.

1442
01:47:55,710 --> 01:47:56,835
In some cases...

1443
